name: 3 Airbus A330s Departing Calgary | Air Canada, KLM, Air Transat ᴴᴰ
description:
Happy Heavy Aircraft Friday!
For today's video, we have 3 Airbus A330s departing Calgary International Airport. For the Air Canada and the Air Transat, I tried a new spot, and I think those videos turned our fairly well, given that there's an excellent view of the rotation. I hope you enjoy!

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
